## Users Service
This project is a microservice API for managing user information, interacting with an external user API.

## Structure
servicio-usuarios/
├── servidor.js # Application entry point.
├── cliente.html # HTML file served for client interaction.
├── package.json
├── package-lock.json
└── .env # File for environment variables (e.g., API_KEY).

## Installation
1. Clone the repository:


git clone https://github.com/Cristina-Colcha/app-tienda.git
cd servicio-usuarios
2. Install dependencies:

npm install axios y express


3. Set up environment variables:

Create a .env file in the root directory of the project and add any necessary environment variables, such as API keys.

API_KEY=YOUR_API_KEY
## Execution
Once installed and configured, you can start the server:

node servidor.js
The service will be accessible at http://localhost:4003.

## API Endpoints
GET /users: Retrieves all users from an external API.
GET /users/:id: Retrieves a specific user by ID.
POST /users: Creates a new user.
PUT /users/:id: Updates a user by ID.
DELETE /users/:id: Deletes a user by ID.
